<plot>Love Lesson is a comedy set in school, where 10 year Amy Bumble has been waiting impatiently for her very first kiss. But who will be the lucky boy? Horrid Miss Dent made a fool of Amy in front of the entire class and no-one wants to be her friend. That is until school heartthrob Alex Handson gives throws her a lifeline. This is it! Amy has read up on how to kiss and she saw her sister in action, but is this enough? Poised to take the next step into the rest of her life with Alex, Amy has it all worked out. But dreams and reality often don't mix and the most unlikely lessons can be learned in school.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344685</url></doc>
